if explanation.entity.negative != null
    |Le conseguenze a lungo termine di un consumo eccessivo di !{explanation.entity.itLabel} possono essere:
    if Array.isArray(explanation.entity.negative)
        eachz negative in explanation.entity.negative with { separator: ',',}
            if Array.isArray(negative.cons_it)
                eachz consequence in negative.cons_it with { separator: ','}
                    |!{consequence}
            else
                |!{negative.cons_it}
    else
        if Array.isArray(explanation.entity.negative.cons_it)
            eachz consequence in explanation.entity.negative.cons_it with { separator: ','}
                    |!{consequence}
        else
            |!{explanation.entity.negative.cons_it}
    |.
